snippet: Angelique Kerber, who had a first-round bye, made a disappointing return to tournament tennis, losing to Zheng Saisai. Simona Halep also lost....
lead_paragraph: Angelique Kerber, who had a first-round bye, made a disappointing return to tournament tennis, losing to Zheng Saisai. Simona Halep also lost.
abstract: Zheng Saisai beats Angelique Kerber in second round at Qatar Open; Stan Wawrinka beats Sergiy Stakhovsky in first round at Dubai Championships.

headline.main: Two Top Seeds Are Ousted in Qatar Open
headline.print_headline: Two Top Seeds Ousted in Qatar Open
